reviewText: The Best Value For All Those Movies!
We've been looking for the adventures of Pluto Nash for a while now. It was a bonus to find it a part of this set with other good Eddie Murphy movies. Each movie had it own disc which was also nice
If your an eddie murphy fan, these are 4 great movies to see.
I like A Thousand Words!!!! Love Imagine That, and Dreamgirls, but the only Eddie Murphy movie I found stupid in this collection is The Adventures of Pluto Nash.
excellent work on all these films

Only bought for the one movie Pluto Nash and received 3 extra movies. Cool opportunity to see more of Eddie Murphy. Downfalls movie selection could have been better . Also no option for Blu Ray left me not wanting it in my collection just an extra movie.
Have not watch the complete dvd
